&lt;li&gt;Provide legal support for project financings and investment transactions, including coordination with lenders, investors, and outside counsel&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support in the development, structuring, negotiation, and execution of key project agreements, including EPC contracts, O&amp;amp;M agreements, and major equipment procurement agreements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with the development, finance, asset management, and operations teams to identify risks and develop practical solutions that advance projects to successful deployment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the management of the company’s contracted portfolio, including negotiation, implementation, and ongoing interpretation of key project and commercial documents&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with and manage external counsel, counterparties, and advisors to efficiently execute transactions and project agreements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
