&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Description:&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;nbsp; This role is a key member of the Finance organization supporting corporate planning, treasury operations, and capital strategy. The Manager of Corporate Planning &amp;amp; Treasury will work closely with the Director of Corporate Planning &amp;amp; Strategy and senior leadership to develop financial insights, support capital raising initiatives, and build scalable treasury capabilities for the company.&amp;nbsp; This role is well-suited for candidates who enjoy solving complex financial problems, building analytical frameworks, and working cross-functionally to support the company’s strategic and capital priorities.&lt;/p&gt;
