&lt;li&gt;Ensure compliance with regulatory requirements, safety standards, and company policies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain project records and technical documents&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare status reports, presentations, and dashboards for management and stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
