&lt;li&gt;Oversee all aspects of the interconnection lifecycle across PJM, NYISO, and ISO-NE, including application strategy, feasibility assessments, system impact studies, facilities studies, cost allocation, milestone compliance, and queue management.&lt;/li&gt;
